theorem closure_inter_self_closure_eq {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure (A ∩ closure A) = closure A := by
  apply subset_antisymm
  · -- `A ∩ closure A` is contained in `closure A`
    have h_subset : (A ∩ closure A : Set X) ⊆ closure A := by
      intro x hx
      exact hx.2
    exact closure_mono h_subset
  · -- `A` is contained in `A ∩ closure A`
    have h_subset : (A : Set X) ⊆ A ∩ closure A := by
      intro x hx
      exact And.intro hx (subset_closure hx)
    have : closure A ⊆ closure (A ∩ closure A) := closure_mono h_subset
    exact this
